d.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/shop-now4.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop-now4\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://iamapeacekeeper.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16750\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Peacekeeper-Causemetics.png?resize=600%2C343\" alt=\"Peacekeeper Causemetics\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Peacekeeper-Causemetics.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Peacekeeper-Causemetics.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. ONE HOPE Wine and Gifts</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.onehopewine.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16821\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/shop.jpg?resize=75%2C20\" alt=\"shop\" width=\"75\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.onehopewine.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16823\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/ONE-HOPE-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C360\" alt=\"ONE HOPE Gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/ONE-HOPE-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/ONE-HOPE-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C180&amp;ssl=1 300w\" size